headline: Illuminating the Hard-to-See Spaces: BLACK+DECKER® Launches dustbuster® reveal™ Product Line with Built-In LED Light Feature
summary: BLACK+DECKER®, a Stanley Black & Decker brand (NYSE: SWK) setting the standard for cordless innovation and home product design, introduces its latest innovation in handheld vacuums, the dustbuster® reveal™ line – one of the brand's most anticipated launches that boasts an LED light to help cleaning enthusiasts easily remove hidden dust and dirt in compact spaces.
